OL,3,CHow to safely dispose of used and
OL,4,Cunused fireworks
OL,6,FResidents in Guernsey are being warned
OL,7,Fof the potential dangers if fireworks
OL,8,Fare not disposed of safely.
OL,10,FGuernsey Waste are reminding islanders
OL,11,Fabout the safe disposal of fireworks
OL,12,Fto avoid putting themselves, waste
OL,13,Fcollection workers and staff at the
OL,14,Ffacilities at risk of harm.
OL,16,FWaste Minimisation Officer Douglas
OL,17,FButton says that it is not only
OL,18,Fcritical to take safety precautions
OL,19,Fseriously during displays, but it is
OL,20,Falso important to dispose of used and
OL,21,Funused fireworks safely.
